node.text: Hey guys - I love these upper body workouts around the cable machine and today we have two exercises that work out our triceps and our back muscles.  These are harder than they look so give it a shot and let me know if it was easy for you or not!  Thanks for following along

node.text: If you have access to a cable machine at your gym you're going to love this workout because it's going to make your arms nice and toned. Today we're going to try some curls that work our biceps and some cable extensions that work the triceps.  Flex those arms!

node.text: We did an earlier episode about warmup stretching but cooling down with a stretch is also a really important part of your workout.  I feel so much better after a little stretch and it's a nice way to close out a day at the gym.  What do you guys think?

node.text: Ladies don't love the idea of working out their upper body and looking too bulky but it's important to create that hourglass figure, create balance in your body, and build strength overall. node.text:
When Ben and I started @be_more_athletics our goal was to help change lives and create a positive community.
The last 5 years at Be More Athletics have been so precious to me. So many memories made, friendships formed and lives changed. Each one special and unique and for that I will always be thankful.

Unfortunately due to the new laws, rules and regulations Be More Athletics will not be reopening after the Covid-19 Shutdown. 💔

We want to give a special THANK YOU and so much love to our talented trainers @metta_world_hayden @keepfit_11 @valeriaalmendaro  @aj.yumul @clintonious_ @yetitube @shaynaholt 
Without you Be More Athletics wouldn’t have been the same.
We want to thank all of our members and anyone who has ever come out to take a class, Bootcamp or just to support us. I’ll forever be grateful to my Be More Athletics Family you changed my life, thank you.

node.text:
My 2 Tips For This Rosy Look 👀 .

1) Blend out the shadow first and add more if you want a darker pigment.
2) Press the brow setter in and up with your finger for a laminated looking brow! It will stay all day 🙌🏼 .
.
Products I used 💐🌷💕 .
Eyes:
@lauramercier Caviar Sticks in the color Violet and Rose Gold
@lauramercier Caviar Volume Panoramic Mascara

Brows:
**Disclaimer, my brows are also microbladed by the talented @jessieserra ** @benefitcosmetics Ka-Brow Pot+Brush (This product is great for filling in your brows and giving defined hair strokes)
@benefitcosmetics 24 Hour Brow Setter (ALL TIME FAVORITE PRODUCT!!) .
.
Lips:
@lauramercier Lip Glacé Wildflower Gloss .
.

#Lauramercire #Benefitcosmetics #Benebabe #makeup #glam #rosy #quarantine #quarantinelife #mua #happyathome #glow #glowingskin #caviarstick 
Song: Roses by SAINt JHN
